CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 24, 1956, pg. A26 reads: "Teen Queen Contest Going Great - With the 1956 Hill Top Teen Queen contest getting into its stride..."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Arneitta Philson wearing necklace and light colored beaded sweater, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Jean Roberts wearing earrings and a striped boatneck shirt, posed for Hill City Teen Queen contest
